# SOPS-encrypted environment variables for CI and builds.
#
# Decrypt with: sops -d .env.enc > .env
# Encrypt with: sops -e .env > .env.enc
#
# The decrypted .env file is gitignored — only the encrypted version is committed.
# CI decrypts at runtime using SOPS_AGE_KEY (stored as a GitHub Actions secret).
#
# Add secrets here as they're needed for tests or builds. Each variable
# follows the pattern: KEY=ENC[AES256_GCM,...]
